                        <locus from="3r" to="16v"/>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (purple tone)</seg>
                        <date notBefore="1800" notAfter="1976">19th/20th century</date>
                        <desc>The handwriting appears uneven. The broadly spaced characters do not
                           rest on the writing line and their height varies (cp. <locus target="#9r"
                           /> with <locus target="#9v"/>). The name of the scribe <persName
                              ref="PRS13274AmIya" role="scribe">ʾAmda ʾIyasus</persName> is
